USING COMMAND LINE ON Hyper:
pwd   (print working directory )

mkdir directoryName  (Make directory )

touch fileName (Create file )

Open file with editor from command line:

atom .  ( textEditor . - opens file with the specified text editor )

node fileName (run file)

node (Puts you in the node, where you can run basic codes directly) 

Ctrl +c exits commandline activities on Hyper